The complaint-filings.parquet file in this folder is the starting point for all the analysis we conducted. The original CSV from which it was derived is too large for GitHub, and just in general (200MB), but can be downloaded from the Data Liberation Project at https://www.data-liberation-project.org/datasets/federal-inmate-complaints/. Once downloaded, we converted it into Parquet format and saved it as complaint-filings.parquet in this folder before running any scripts.
